'''凯西·希尔顿'''（{{lang-en|Kathy Hilton}}，{{bd|1959年|3月13日}}），[[美国|美国]]女演员、社会名流、時尚設計師與慈善家<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2007/12/kathy_hilton_to_invade_fashion.html |title=New York Magazine |accessdate=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2017-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171112021100/http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2007/12/kathy_hilton_to_invade_fashion.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2008/08/kathy_hilton_to_mccain_no_your.html |title=New York Magazine |accessdate=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2017-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171111205025/http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2008/08/kathy_hilton_to_mccain_no_your.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="latimesstory">Booth Moore, [http://www.latimes.com/features/image/la-ig-hilton-20121209,0,7987268.story Special occasion calls for a twist with Kathy Hilton] {{Wayback|url=http://www.latimes.com/features/image/la-ig-hilton-20121209,0,7987268.story |date=20121210061155 }}, ''[[The_Los_Angeles_Times|The Los Angeles Times]]'', 2012-12-09</ref><ref name="ownlatoya">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oprah.com/own-life-with-latoya/Life-With-La-Toya-Kathy-Hilton |title=Ophrah Winfrey Network: Life With La Toya |accessdate=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714213610/http://www.oprah.com/own-life-with-latoya/Life-With-La-Toya-Kathy-Hilton |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她是社交名流[[帕丽斯·希尔顿|帕丽斯·希尔顿]]和時尚設計師[[妮琪·希尔顿|妮琪·希尔顿]]的母亲<ref name="latimesstory"/>。

== 早年 ==
凱西·希爾頓的父母是羅倫斯·K·阿瓦奇諾（Laurence K. Avanzino；1935年－1997年）和凱斯琳·杜根（Kathleen Dugan；1938年－2002年），出生不久后父母离婚，母亲改嫁给了肯尼斯·埃德溫·理查茲（Kenneth Edwin Richards；1917年－1998年）。母親凱斯琳與第二任丈夫生下了{{Link-en|金·理查兹|Kim Richards}}與[[凱爾·理查兹|凱爾·理查兹]]，即凱西同母異父的妹妹們，兩人後來都成為了童星演員<ref name="latimesstory"/>。除了她們二人以外，凱西另外還有五個同父異母的手足們。她身上流有義大利裔、愛爾蘭裔及蘇格蘭裔血統<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=6pd84XvouoQC&pg=PT32&q=%22The+first+of+her+mostly+horrific+unions%E2%80%94essentially+a+shotgun+wedding%E2%80%94was+to+a+bad+boy+named+Larry+Avanzino%2C+an+Italian-American%2C+who+had+gotten+the+pretty+Irish-American+Dugan+girl+pregnant+in+the+backseat+of+her+1957+black+Chevrolet+convertible.%22 |title=Jerry Oppenheimer, ''House of Hilton'', Crown Publishing, 2006 |access-date=2022-06-03 |archive-date=2022-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220135316/https://books.google.ca/books?id=6pd84XvouoQC&pg=PT32&q=%22The%20first%20of%20her%20mostly%20horrific%20unions%E2%80%94essentially%20a%20shotgun%20wedding%E2%80%94was%20to%20a%20bad%20boy%20named%20Larry%20Avanzino%2C%20an%20Italian-American%2C%20who%20had%20gotten%20the%20pretty%20Irish-American%20Dugan%20girl%20pregnant%20in%20the%20backseat%20of%20her%201957%20black%20Chevrolet%20convertible.%22 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/projo/access/31911812.html?dids=31911812:31911812&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Feb+20%2C+1997&author=&pub=The+Providence+Journal&desc=Providence+LAURENCE+K.+AVANZINO&pqatl=google |title=Providence Journal |accessdate=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2012-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107125020/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/projo/access/31911812.html?dids=31911812:31911812&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Feb+20%2C+1997&author=&pub=The+Providence+Journal&desc=Providence+LAURENCE+K.+AVANZINO&pqatl=google |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/projo/access/39692575.html?dids=39692575:39692575&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Mar+12%2C+1999&author=&pub=The+Providence+Journal&desc=Narragansett+ELIZABETH+J.+AVANZINO&pqatl=google |title=Providence Journal |accessdate=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2012-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107125038/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/projo/access/39692575.html?dids=39692575:39692575&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Mar+12%2C+1999&author=&pub=The+Providence+Journal&desc=Narragansett+ELIZABETH+J.+AVANZINO&pqatl=google |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

她畢業於洛杉磯一間私立高中，在校期間與[[麥可·傑克森|麥可·傑克森]]成為了好友。在他[[麥可·傑克森之死|逝世]]之前，她一直都與傑克森維持著親密的友誼關係<ref>[http://nymag.com/news/features/childhood/paris-nicky-hilton-2013-4/ "The Hilton Sisters"] {{Wayback|url=http://nymag.com/news/features/childhood/paris-nicky-hilton-2013-4/ |date=20160501170957 }}. ''New York Magazine''. 2013-03-31.</ref>。

==个人生活==
凯西·希尔顿和[[希尔顿酒店|希尔顿酒店]]的继承人{{Link-en|理查·希爾頓|Richard Hilton}}在1979年11月24日结婚。他们有四个孩子：
*[[帕丽斯·希尔顿|帕丽斯·希尔顿]]（1981年2月17日出生）
*[[妮琪·希尔顿|妮琪·希尔顿]]（1983年10月5日出生）
* 巴倫·希爾頓二世（1989年11月7日出生）
* 康拉德·修斯·希爾頓三世（1994年3月3日出生）

